node.text:
I'm really feeling the obscure colours on cars at the moment, I felt like this lowered GT40 fit really well with the not so obvious @kmcwheels 720, they look like Steelies, was gonna throw them on a D-type jag but this just worked for me 😂.
-
-
Slowly getting back into the rhythm of creating again, after what feels like a few months of a creative block/stumble. But feeling good and ready to create some sick shiz again!
-
-
Let me know if there's any particular cars i haven't done yet or in a while you'd like to see!
-

A short collection of some of my favourite shots I was able to get at @fosgoodwood, featuring @singervehicledesign, @glickenhaus, @porsche_gb, @toyotauk, @jamesdeane130, @lamborghini, @bmwuk, @astonmartinlagonda & others!
-
-
Let me know which is your favourite shot below!

Photography is just a hobbie for me, I find it to be a bit of an escape from being behind a desk 24/7, a situation for real world renders, trying to make most of the situation happening around to get a shot that is passable 😂. I have so many photos I've never posted, but would definitely love to do so!

node.text:
Ok, so, what do we all think of the new @lotuscars EMIRA?! Give me them opinions!

A £60k, 400bhp, V6 (for now) mid-engined sports car, and honestly it's bloody beautiful! It sounds sick as well!
-
-
I had the opportunity to spend my time at @fosgoodwood
With Lotus these last two days and seeing the reaction and interest to the Emira was MEGA! It's basically styled like the Evija as well which is a huge win in my mind!
-
-
I need one. I also need to modify one...😂
-
-
Massive thanks to the hospitality @lotuscars & @lotuspr
-

A week ago I popped over to @wheelpros_europe for a bit of 1-1 time with the MK2 Thunderbunny designed by myself & brought to life by the mad genius that is @jeanpierrekraemer.

Making @players_jay & @players_rik (mainly Rikki) actually do some work and drive this thing out so I could shoot it 😂. Such a special thing to see, i managed to get some shots of it  with my RX7 along with other detail shots which I'll post seperately!
-
-
I highly recommend you visit @caffeineandmachine this Saturday for the @rotiform event, you'll see this there! ;) ❤
